cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with interactive object segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves the use of deep learning models (cs.AI) and large-scale annotation campaigns (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the design space of interactive segmentation models, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the paper deals with the OpenImages dataset, which is a multimedia dataset (cs.MM).
